## Executive Summary  
Comprehensive technical analysis of telemedicine implementation in Buryatia Republic, demonstrating systematic methodology for healthcare digital transformation in remote regions.

## Technical Analysis Methodology

### Data Collection Framework
- **Geospatial Mapping**: GIS analysis of 21 districts with connectivity metrics
- **Healthcare Infrastructure Inventory**: Quantitative assessment of medical facilities
- **Network Performance Metrics**: Internet bandwidth and reliability measurements
